      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AUSSIE RAVEN (2) was sent out long odds last time but rocketed out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 7 length third (25.72) over 450m at Ballarat. Can go on with it. LITTLE MISS MAY (3) has been in sparkling form recording back to back wins, the latest at Warrnambool last time over 390m in (22.57). Hard to fault her recent form and can win again. ASTON KILLARA (6) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at this track over 400m behind Aston Haruto (23.20) in a Rank Limit - Restricted Win. Was in the money the start prior. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Deserves plenty of respect. CINDY SIYAN (1) was below best last time at Warragul (23.93) in a Mix 6/7, finishing a 25 length eighth. Has two wins already from this draw.",
